metadata.name: Circle Notation by Moonzart #1
metadata.description:
Starting with red, imagine a deep and rich shade that evokes feelings of passion and intensity. Moving on to orange, the tone becomes warmer and more inviting, reminding us of the sunsets and sunrises. The yellow tone is bright and cheerful, reminiscent of sunshine and happiness.

As we move towards the cooler tones, the green shade is a refreshing and calming color that reminds us of nature and growth. The blue tone is tranquil and peaceful, resembling the ocean or the sky. Lastly, the purple and pink shades are delicate and romantic, creating a sense of whimsy and playfulness.
